                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179001130009"></xptr>The prisoner Damant was <rs id="t17900113-3-verdict19" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900113-3-verdict19" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
